{"tid":2090480,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台F-16演習模擬轟炸登陸船","createTime":"2020-07-02T07:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T09:10:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7554087e3edf817f0284dd59c77d49d8a5f70219","tid":2090480,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:47:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200702/LOUBLERYRSP2FG4VW2LOWFYK7Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200702%2FLOUBLERYRSP2FG4VW2LOWFYK7Y%2F&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8FcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=2f2c07a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200702%2FLOUBLERYRSP2FG4VW2LOWFYK7Y%2F&h=04f3d9a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200702/LOUBLERYRSP2FG4VW2LOWFYK7Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n台F-16演習模擬轟炸登陸船<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9ScFTW0ULOzpoCCuW0nf6sDPdjk=/190x80/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NUFYNFM3CEYSTPOBA7NDTCAZCE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9ScFTW0ULOzpoCCuW0nf6sDPdjk%3D%2F190x80%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNUFYNFM3CEYSTPOBA7NDTCAZCE.gif&h=e4395137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台海空域近日不斷有中國大陸、美國軍機輪番現身，氣氛越趨緊張。台灣軍方近日加強演練，空軍花蓮基地昨晨7時出動八架F-16戰機（圖），每架掛載兩枚2,000磅通用炸彈，模擬轟炸敵方登陸船。此外，台灣海軍劍龍級潛艦，昨在東南海域演練試射德製SUT重型魚雷，以除役的諾克斯級巡防艦編號936「海陽」號為靶船。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n潛艦試射德製魚雷<br />\n<br />\n據台媒報道，漢光36號實兵實彈演習將在7月13日至17日舉行，16日在台中甲南海灘進行聯合反登陸實兵實彈操演。台軍為準備漢光演習，空軍花蓮基地昨晨已開始演練，四架<br />\n.................................<br />\n架F-16分批返航，圓滿達成轟炸任務。這次轟炸任務由俗稱「小紅」、編號6677的彩繪機領軍，尾翼上有「紅色太陽神」圖騰。<br />\n<br />\n另據台軍官員透露，昨清晨4時至8時，海軍劍龍級潛艦在東南海域演練試射德製SUT重型魚雷，以除役的諾克斯級巡防艦編號936「海陽」號為目標，這次試射與F-16轟炸演練有一定關連，但事涉機密不便透露詳情。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"8ab7452306ffa20e5c9ac6021b0351188255beb5","tid":2090480,"uid":41154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:53:38.000Z","msg":"Taiwan No.1"},{"pid":"dfdbafcf7448f10ff2ad6607f9bb1f1637305fc2","tid":2090480,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6cf02afaf708da7bb2a08ebd9f907877c953bf","tid":2090480,"uid":75994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:56:12.000Z","msg":"支持一個中<span style=\"color: gold;\">華民</span>國統一"},{"pid":"74b0e35f76798200ff1d173900381a0a34cf55ff","tid":2090480,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:57:46.000Z","msg":"炸條撚咩<br />\n大陸啲舢舨過到台灣海峽再算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64dcbc13732867506f25325dce9ea1a01a30ca7f","tid":2090480,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:58:38.000Z","msg":"整返個「小英」魚雷"},{"pid":"e31276e8b0deb769633b11d7a7ef99efe32b1c14","tid":2090480,"uid":167597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74b0e35f76798200ff1d173900381a0a34cf55ff","tid":2090480,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:57:46.000Z","msg":"炸條撚咩<br />\n大陸啲舢舨過到台灣海峽再算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:08:33.000Z","msg":"琴日聽節目講，一粒重型魚雷就可以收巡洋艦皮。<br />\n一打中龍骨架船會跳離水面，跟著就即刻沈"},{"pid":"47cd70dabebe031a91793239306c30eba88e5478","tid":2090480,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:10:44.000Z","msg":"早幾日大規模調動雄三